des: The Galveston Guide is a custom skill intended to share the favorite spots of a frequent traveler to Galveston Texas. Whether you have vacationed to the area for years, are new to the gulf island community or are just passing through, we have all the best spots in Galveston curated into one handy resource. Check it out and we hope you enjoy a little food and fun in our favorite vacation spots in Galveston!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
